gctWiMAX: RUN

 $ sudo gctwimax -h

Usage: ./gctwimax [options]
Options:
  -C, --cfg-file=FILE         path to configuration file
      --dl-xml=FILE           DL XML Image & exit
  -D,                         Switch device & exit
  -v,                         verbose log level (even more -vv)
  -p, --pid-file=FILE         PID file (only for daemonize mode)
  -d, --daemonize             daemonize after startup
  -V, --version               print the version number
      --with-dbus             Run with dbus support
  -h, --help                  display this help
  

 $ gctwimax --cfg-file=/usr/share/gctwimax/gctwimax.conf
 
If the driver did not get IP Address automatically enter:
 $ dhclient wimaxX